BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:\n        <p>Join us for a delicious celebration of Bitcoin Pizza Day\, brought to you by PizzaDAO! 🍕💸</p>\n<p>On this historic day\, we honor the legendary first real-world Bitcoin transaction: when Laszlo Hanyecz paid 10\,000 BTC for two pizzas in 2010. That single cheesy exchange ignited a worldwide movement and earned a permanent slice in crypto history!</p>\n<p>Join us for a delicious celebration of Bitcoin Pizza Day\, brought to you by PizzaDAO! 🍕💸\nOn this historic day\, we honor the legendary first real-world Bitcoin transaction: when Laszlo Hanyecz paid 10\,000 BTC for two pizzas in 2010. That single cheesy exchange ignited a worldwide movement and earned a permanent slice in crypto history!\n🔥 <strong>What to Expect:</strong>\n✅ <strong>Casual networking</strong> – Meet fellow crypto enthusiasts\, builders\, and investors.\n✅ DeFi Demo – Presentation by local web3 developer who has built up $5 million in TVL\n✅ <strong>Good vibes\, great beer</strong> – No pitches\, no panels\, just <strong>fun and great conversation</strong> over drinks.\n🚗 <strong>Heads up: Parking is street parking only\, so plan accordingly!</strong></p>\n        \n        <p><b>Event Link:</b> <a href="https://www.meetup.com/baltimore-cryptomondays/events/307624661/">https://www.meetup.com/baltimore-cryptomondays/events/307624661/</a></p>\n        \n        
DTEND:20250523T003000Z
LOCATION:Joe Benny's\, 313 S High St\, Baltimore\, MD US
DTSTART:20250522T223000Z
SUMMARY:Bitcoin Pizza Day Party with PizzaDAO
UID:81fd2c62-8509-410d-8034-b889312a187e@81fd.org
URL:https://www.meetup.com/baltimore-cryptomondays/events/307624661/
END:VEVENT
